'''Shurandy Ruggerio Sambo''' (born 19 August 2001) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|right back]] for {{English football  updater|Burnley}} club [[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]. Born in the Netherlands, he represents the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].

==Club career==
===PSV===
Sambo played youth football for SV Braakhuizen and [[PSV Eindhoven]]. In the winter break of the [[2019–20 PSV Eindhoven season|2019–20 season]], he was promoted to the reserve team, [[Jong PSV]], competing in the second-tier [[Eerste Divisie]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Shurandy Sambo over zijn eerste maanden bij Jong PSV |url=https://www.psv.nl/nieuwspagina/artikel/shurandy-sambo-over-zijn-eerste-maanden-bij-jong-psv.htm |website=PSV |access-date=5 August 2022 |language=nl-NL |date=23 May 2020}}</ref> He made his debut on 13 January 2020 in a 0–0 league draw at home against [[Jong Ajax]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Elfrink |first1=Rik |title=Shurandy Sambo wil bij PSV doorbreken: Nu op jacht naar meer |url=https://www.ed.nl/psv/shurandy-sambo-wil-bij-psv-doorbreken-nu-op-jacht-naar-meer~a92dcd09/ |access-date=5 August 2022 |work=Eindhovens Dagblad |date=13 January 2020 |language=nl}}</ref>

In the [[2020–21 Eerste Divisie|2020–21 season]], Sambo made 35 appearances for Jong PSV, scoring six goals.<ref name="SW" /> He made his debut for the first team in the final matchday of the [[Eredivisie]] on 16 May 2021, coming off the bench for [[Armando Obispo]] in the 77th minute against [[FC Utrecht|Utrecht]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ottens |first1=Chris |title=Sambo annuleerde vakantie naar Curaçao voor PSV-debuut: Vroegen of ik nog in het land was |url=https://www.ed.nl/psv/sambo-annuleerde-vakantie-naar-curacao-voor-psv-debuut-vroegen-of-ik-nog-in-het-land-was~aa471688/ |access-date=5 August 2022 |work=Eindhovens Dagblad |date=16 May 2021 |language=nl}}</ref>

On 15 August 2021, Sambo [[Anterior cruciate ligament injury|tore his anterior cruciate ligament]] during practice, sidelining him for the entire [[2021–22 Eredivisie|2021–22 season]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Persoonlijk drama voor PSV'er Sambo: seizoen voorbij door knieblessure |url=https://www.vi.nl/nieuws/persoonlijk-drama-voor-psver-sambo-seizoen-voorbij-door-knieblessure |access-date=5 August 2022 |work=Voetbal International |date=15 August 2021 |language=nl}}</ref> At the end of the season, on 28 April 2022, he extended his contract with PSV until 2024.<ref>{{cite web |title=PSV verlengt contract Shurandy Sambo |url=https://www.psv.nl/nieuwspagina/artikel/psv-verlengt-contract-shurandy-sambo.htm |website=PSV |access-date=5 August 2022 |language=nl-NL |date=28 April 2022}}</ref>

====Sparta Rotterdam (loan)====
Sambo joined [[Eredivisie]] club [[Sparta Rotterdam]] on loan for the [[2022–23 Eredivisie|2022–23 season]], with an option to buy.<ref>{{cite web |title=Sparta huurt Sambo van PSV |url=https://www.sparta-rotterdam.nl/sparta-huurt-sambo-psv/ |website=Sparta Rotterdam |access-date=5 August 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220805181511/https://www.sparta-rotterdam.nl/sparta-huurt-sambo-psv/ |archive-date=5 August 2022 |language=nl |date=4 August 2022 |url-status=live}}</ref>

===Burnley===
On 28 June 2024, Sambo signed for [[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]] on a four-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=Burnley sign ex-PSV defender Sambo|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/c3grldrr1jgo |website=BBC Sport |access-date=24 August 2024 |language=nl-ENG |date=28 June 2024}}</ref>

==International career==
Born in the Netherlands, Sambo is of Curaçaoan descent. He is a youth international for the Netherlands. He was called up to the preliminary squad for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]] for the [[2021 CONCACAF Gold Cup]].<ref name=":0">{{cite web|date=18 June 2021|title=2021 Concacaf Gold Cup preliminary rosters announced|url=https://www.concacaf.com/gold-cup/article/2021-concacaf-gold-cup-preliminary-rosters-announced/|access-date=19 June 2021|publisher=CONCACAF}}</ref>

On 29 August 2025, Sambo's request to change sports citizenship from Dutch to Curaçaoan was approved by [[FIFA]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://knowledge.fifa.com/change-of-association-platform|title=FIFA Change of Association Platform|website=knowledge.fifa.com|date=29 August 2025|accessdate=30 August 2025}}</ref> He made his debut for Curaçao on 6 September 2025 in a 0-0 draw against [[Trinidad and Tobago national football team|Trinidad and Tobago]].

